# Event Ticket Booking Platform (MERN Microservices)

**Roles:** Customer | Admin | (Optional) Event Organizer

---

# 👤 Member 1 – User Service + Booking Service

## 🔹 User Service

**Responsibility:** Authentication, authorization, and user management.

**Roles Managed:** Customer, Admin, Organizer (optional)

### Customer

- Register, Login
- View & update profile
- View own bookings
- Delete account

### Admin

- View all users
- Change roles
- Deactivate users

### Organizer (Optional)

- Manage own events
- View bookings for own events

**Integrations:**
Booking, Review, and Payment services validate users via JWT.

---

## 🔹 Booking Service

**Responsibility:** Core ticket booking logic.

### Customer

- Book tickets
- Cancel own booking
- View booking history & details

### Admin

- View all bookings
- Cancel any booking
- Monitor booking activity

**Booking Flow:**

1. Validate JWT (User Service)
2. Check availability (Event Service)
3. Create booking (pending)
4. Call Payment Service
5. Update booking status
6. Reporting Service collects data

---

# 👤 Member 2 – Event Service

**Responsibility:** Event management & ticket inventory.

### Customer

- View events
- Search/filter events
- View event details
- See ticket availability
- View average rating

### Admin

- Create, update, delete events
- Set ticket count & price

### Organizer (Optional)

- Manage own events only

**Integrations:**
Booking (availability check), Review (event validation), Reporting (event data).

---

# 👤 Member 3 – Payment + Notification Service

## 🔹 Payment Service

**Responsibility:** Simulated payment processing & transaction management.

### Customer

- Pay for booking
- View payment history
- Retry failed payment

### Admin

- View transactions
- Monitor failures
- View revenue summary

**Flow:**
Receives request → validates booking → processes payment → updates booking → triggers notification.

---

## 🔹 Notification

**Responsibility:** System alerts.

### Customer

- Booking confirmation
- Payment success/failure
- Cancellation notice

### Admin

- Failed payment alerts
- High booking alerts

Triggered by Booking & Payment services.

---

# 👤 Member 4 – Feedback & Review + Reporting Service

## 🔹 Review Service

**Responsibility:** Ratings and reviews.

### Customer

- Add/update/delete review
- Rate events (1–5 stars)
- View reviews

### Admin

- Remove inappropriate reviews
- Moderate content

**Integrations:** Validate user (User Service) and event (Event Service).

---

## 🔹 Reporting Service

**Responsibility:** System analytics.

### Customer

- Personal booking summary
- Personal spending summary

### Admin

- Total revenue
- Popular events
- Tickets sold per event
- Revenue per event
- Booking trends
- Active users

**Integrations:** Fetch data from Booking, Payment, and Event services.

---

# 🔐 Role Access Summary

| Feature         | Customer | Admin | Organizer      |
| --------------- | -------- | ----- | -------------- |
| Register/Login  | ✅       | ✅    | ✅             |
| Create Event    | ❌       | ✅    | Own only       |
| Book Ticket     | ✅       | ❌    | ❌             |
| Cancel Booking  | Own      | Any   | ❌             |
| Process Payment | ✅       | ❌    | ❌             |
| Add Review      | ✅       | ❌    | ❌             |
| Delete Review   | ❌       | ✅    | ❌             |
| View Reports    | Limited  | Full  | Event-specific |

---

# 🏗 Final Architecture Distribution

- **Member 1:** User + Booking
- **Member 2:** Event
- **Member 3:** Payment + Notification
- **Member 4:** Review + Reporting

